</li>
<li>
    We may use your personal information, including date of birth, to verify identity and to assist with identification of users.
</li>
<li>
    From time to time, we may use your personal information to send important notices, such as communications about purchases and changes to our terms, conditions, and policies because this information is important to your interection with us.
</li>
<li>
