<li>
    We understand the importance of taking extra precautions to protect the privacy and safety of children using our products and services. To prove that, in the case that we learn that we have collected the personal information of a child under 13, or equivalent minimum age depending on jurisdiction, we will take steps to delete the information as soon as possible.
</li>

